OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784211519
OL,3,CHundreds of shoplifting offences
OL,4,Cidentified via crime reporting app
OL,6,FMore than 600 shoplifting offences
OL,7,Fhave been identified through a new
OL,8,Fcrime reporting app which is being
OL,9,Ftrialled in Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,10,FWight.
OL,12,FThe UKPAC application, which was
OL,13,Flaunched across the counties last
OL,14,Fyear, allows shop staff to report
OL,15,Fincidents quickly on their mobile
OL,16,Fphones.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
