PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784211519
OL,3,CHundreds of shoplifting offences
OL,4,Cidentified via crime reporting app
OL,6,FA 12-month trial was introduced by the
OL,7,Farea's Police and Crime Commissioner,
OL,8,FDonna Jones, and has seen around 1,500
OL,9,Fcompanies and 3,000 individual users
OL,10,Faccess it.
OL,12,FCommisioner Jones hailed the app as a
OL,13,F"vital tool in tackling the scourge of
OL,14,Fshoplifting in our towns and cities".
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
