OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784211519
OL,3,CHundreds of shoplifting offences
OL,4,Cidentified via crime reporting app
OL,6,FThe software has saved more than 2,500
OL,7,Fhours of police time from paperwork,
OL,8,Fwith individuals able to send in CCTV
OL,9,Fthemselves rather than request a visit
OL,10,Ffrom officers.
OL,12,FIt's led to 181 offenders being
OL,13,Fcharged and a combined 62 years' worth
OL,14,Fof custodial sentences being handed
OL,15,Fout.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
