CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784211519
OL,3,CHundreds of shoplifting offences
OL,4,Cidentified via crime reporting app
OL,6,FSome 22 Criminal Behaviour Orders
OL,7,F(CBO) have also been issued to
OL,8,Fprolific offenders while the number of
OL,9,Fcases seeing formal action taken (FAT
OL,10,Frate) currently sits at 58% - which is
OL,11,F22% above the Force average.
OL,13,FThe app has now been selected by 10
OL,14,Fforces across the UK, following on
OL,15,Ffrom the success in Hampshire and the
OL,16,FIsle of Wight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
